DEP Operational Goal:
SID requirement for Noise abatement
Flights with RFL between FL100 and FL200 are expected to use SID NETEX.
Flights with RFL at or above FL210 shall file SIDs MODRU (H/J/T/Z). These flights are eligible to leave SID MODRU at NETEX if destination is in the south-west and they file the RAD ANNEX 3B DCTs  NETEX - DELOM or NETEX - RASCA. All other traffic shall continue until MODRU.
